Subject: [R-sig-eco] Testing the difference between fractions in RDA
In-Reply-To: <COL101-DS138E214E6207DB46EC73BCCFB10@phx.gbl>
References: <COL101-DS138E214E6207DB46EC73BCCFB10@phx.gbl>
